text: Leptenicodes quadrilineatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1953. It is known from New Caledonia.BioLib.cz - Leptenicodes quadrilineatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1953
